overview: Join the Rocfish gang as they present the exciting tale of Jonah through action packed songs and dance. See Roxi and the team explore the exciting world under the sea at Queensland's Underwater World and join in all the fun with Rocfish and their friends at the beach.  And watch out for your face on video as Rocfish take it to the parks and playgrounds around the country to see what Aussie kids think about all kinds of stuff!
title: A Whale Of A Tale
